WEBVTT

01:30.920 --> 01:35.000
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:35.830 --> 01:39.259
[2005]

01:41.640 --> 01:42.710
The movement is broken.

01:42.710 --> 01:44.110
It can't drive the gears.

01:44.280 --> 01:45.759
Can it be repaired?

01:46.200 --> 01:47.310
I can pay any price.

01:47.710 --> 01:49.110
It's not about the money.

01:49.640 --> 01:50.950
It's imported,

01:51.000 --> 01:52.070
and it's been discontinued for years.

01:52.070 --> 01:53.229
The parts aren't available anymore.

01:53.229 --> 01:54.430
It can't be repaired.

01:54.509 --> 01:55.350
It's not expensive.

01:55.350 --> 01:56.350
Just buy a new one.

02:00.390 --> 02:01.250
Thank you, sir.

02:04.010 --> 02:07.350
[Episode 36: The Gears of Fate]

02:12.400 --> 02:13.280
Xia Xiaolan!

02:14.590 --> 02:15.800
I know you're nearby.

02:16.190 --> 02:17.079
Come out!

02:18.430 --> 02:20.030
You only play tricks, right?

02:20.400 --> 02:21.730
Do you think I'm scared?

02:22.310 --> 02:23.040
I won't lose!

02:23.520 --> 02:25.079
You will never beat me!

02:25.079 --> 02:26.079
Come out!

02:26.630 --> 02:27.400
Come out!

02:28.000 --> 02:29.420
Don't you want to catch me?

02:29.420 --> 02:30.210
Come out!

02:30.240 --> 02:30.870
Come out!

02:30.340 --> 02:33.030
[Shengcheng Commercial Bank]

02:31.030 --> 02:31.470
Ma'am,

02:31.760 --> 02:32.280
if you keep making a scene,

02:32.280 --> 02:33.480
I'll call the police.

02:49.000 --> 02:50.660
Du Chengrong's men have left.

02:50.750 --> 02:51.410
Shall we go?

02:52.360 --> 02:52.890
Let's go.

02:57.310 --> 02:58.150
Hello.

02:58.710 --> 02:59.970
I have a case to report.

03:00.470 --> 03:02.520
The mastermind
behind the wedding banquet poisoning

03:02.520 --> 03:05.120
appeared near the old shipyard
in Shengcheng.

03:09.030 --> 03:09.750
Xia Ziyu,

03:10.890 --> 03:11.950
you should go back.

04:04.710 --> 04:05.910
Have you got the money ready?

04:05.910 --> 04:07.960
Can you guarantee I'll get to Kong Island?

04:07.960 --> 04:09.630
Will I have a place to stay
when I get there?

04:09.630 --> 04:11.690
Why are you talking so much nonsense?

04:11.750 --> 04:13.080
Do you want to go or not?

04:13.270 --> 04:14.630
If not, don't waste time.

04:14.630 --> 04:16.560
Many people want to get on the boat.

04:16.829 --> 04:17.240
Jeez.

04:18.240 --> 04:18.920
I want to go.

04:21.800 --> 04:22.600
Wait a minute.

04:41.000 --> 04:42.480
Wait for my message tonight.

04:42.480 --> 04:43.680
We'll leave anytime.

04:57.659 --> 05:00.780
[Attack Case on Yunan Province's
Top Science Student]

05:31.070 --> 05:31.870
Xia Xiaolan,

05:33.230 --> 05:34.430
you're finally here.

05:35.440 --> 05:36.240
Young Master!

05:36.390 --> 05:36.920
Here!

05:46.470 --> 05:47.750
Xia Ziyu's parents

05:47.750 --> 05:49.240
have been sent to the guesthouse.

05:49.240 --> 05:50.360
But she has a younger brother

05:50.360 --> 05:51.290
named Xia Junbao.

05:51.290 --> 05:52.159
We couldn't find him.

05:52.159 --> 05:53.220
Couldn't find him?

05:53.560 --> 05:54.159
He's a grown man.

05:54.159 --> 05:55.390
How could you not find him?

05:55.390 --> 05:56.630
Xia Junbao has been living in Shengcheng

05:56.630 --> 05:57.630
for so many years.

05:57.800 --> 05:59.360
He's very familiar with this place.

05:59.360 --> 06:01.090
I guess someone is helping him.

06:01.360 --> 06:02.070
He's a little kid.

06:02.070 --> 06:03.130
Who would help him?

06:03.400 --> 06:04.070
It must be

06:04.070 --> 06:05.310
Ke Yixiong's men.

06:06.190 --> 06:07.950
That loser is really in Shengcheng?

06:07.950 --> 06:08.800
I think so.

06:08.920 --> 06:10.360
Xia Ziyu has been keeping him hidden

06:10.360 --> 06:11.760
in Kong Island all along.

06:13.110 --> 06:14.240
How many men do we have in Shengcheng?

06:14.240 --> 06:15.240
Call them all out.

06:15.310 --> 06:15.950
Young Master,

06:15.950 --> 06:16.750
since you said

06:16.770 --> 06:17.920
you wouldn't do anything illegal,

06:17.920 --> 06:20.050
they all left to work for other bosses.

06:21.630 --> 06:23.490
How many men does the old man have?

06:23.560 --> 06:24.680
Master only ordered

06:24.680 --> 06:25.880
Xia Ziyu to be killed.

06:25.950 --> 06:26.560
He doesn't want to get involved

06:26.560 --> 06:28.420
in her business with Xia Xiaolan.

06:30.720 --> 06:31.980
If you come with us now,

06:32.360 --> 06:35.020
it can still be considered
turning yourself in.

06:36.390 --> 06:37.450
Turning myself in?

06:39.680 --> 06:40.830
For what?

06:42.720 --> 06:43.190
Xia Xiaolan,

06:43.190 --> 06:44.159
this man you chose

06:44.159 --> 06:45.190
is just as naive

06:47.070 --> 06:47.670
as you are.

06:48.720 --> 06:50.320
But I still have to thank you.

06:50.800 --> 06:51.870
With your naivety

06:52.310 --> 06:53.770
and self-righteousness,

06:55.680 --> 06:56.800
I'm sure you've taken good care

06:56.800 --> 06:57.630
of my parents

06:59.270 --> 07:00.530
and my brother, right?

07:01.120 --> 07:02.240
Not very well.

07:03.040 --> 07:03.870
But if they are all as

07:03.870 --> 07:04.930
capable as Hongxia

07:05.240 --> 07:06.590
and willing to stay on the right path,

07:06.590 --> 07:07.480
at least they can live

07:07.480 --> 07:08.280
a normal life.

07:08.310 --> 07:09.480
A normal life?

07:12.040 --> 07:14.170
Who doesn't want to live a normal life?

07:15.390 --> 07:17.390
Xia Xiaolan, do you know this place?

07:18.270 --> 07:19.510
It was right here

07:20.480 --> 07:21.510
that I lost everything

07:21.510 --> 07:22.800
that belonged to me.

07:24.000 --> 07:24.830
My identity,

07:26.240 --> 07:27.070
my name,

07:28.360 --> 07:30.190
my hometown, and my home.

07:31.560 --> 07:32.159
Do you know

07:33.159 --> 07:35.120
how I survived 10 years

07:35.120 --> 07:36.560
of living in fear?

07:42.070 --> 07:44.270
At that time, I liked the night the most.

07:45.800 --> 07:46.870
Because I could stand here

07:46.870 --> 07:48.950
and look at the lights across the river.

07:48.950 --> 07:50.190
I looked,

07:51.800 --> 07:54.200
while imagining the life
on the other side.

07:55.000 --> 07:57.260
I thought as long as
I could make it there,

07:58.000 --> 07:59.330
I would live a good life.

08:00.480 --> 08:02.070
But for many years after,

08:04.680 --> 08:06.280
I became afraid of the night.

08:07.800 --> 08:09.130
I was afraid of the dark.

08:11.460 --> 08:13.660
I was afraid of returning to this place.

08:18.470 --> 08:20.070
All of this is because of you.

08:20.430 --> 08:22.760
You are the one
who made me end up like this!

08:24.240 --> 08:24.970
Are you done?

08:29.310 --> 08:30.440
After so many years,

08:31.040 --> 08:32.500
you haven't changed a bit.

08:34.000 --> 08:35.530
You still push all the blame

08:36.320 --> 08:37.360
onto others.

08:37.909 --> 08:38.549
Xia Ziyu,

08:39.720 --> 08:41.450
did I make you achieve nothing?

08:42.720 --> 08:44.520
Did I make you lose your dignity?

08:45.670 --> 08:46.630
All of this

08:47.750 --> 08:49.350
started with your jealousy.

08:50.360 --> 08:51.910
You ended up like this

08:53.120 --> 08:53.630
because

08:53.630 --> 08:55.830
you've always wanted to rely on others.

08:57.000 --> 08:57.720
Cousin,

08:59.000 --> 09:00.600
you are actually very smart.

09:02.100 --> 09:04.030
You could have had a better future.

09:11.030 --> 09:11.790
Xia Xiaolan,

09:13.120 --> 09:14.450
do you think you will...

09:15.670 --> 09:17.000
have a better future?

09:20.360 --> 09:21.030
Granny Yu.

09:23.790 --> 09:24.990
What brings you here?

09:25.270 --> 09:25.600
Granny Yu,

09:25.600 --> 09:26.440
I'm here to see Auntie Fen.

09:26.440 --> 09:27.240
Is she at home?

09:28.550 --> 09:30.150
Then you have to wait a while.

09:30.270 --> 09:31.600
She hasn't arrived yet.

09:33.340 --> 09:34.340
At this hour?

09:35.670 --> 09:36.510
That's weird.

09:37.200 --> 09:38.120
I know you and your mom

09:38.120 --> 09:39.150
are very close.

09:40.440 --> 09:42.040
At such an important moment,

09:42.670 --> 09:44.530
how could she not be here with you?

09:46.080 --> 09:47.240
Go! Go!

09:48.390 --> 09:49.110
Xiaolan!

09:49.360 --> 09:49.750
Mom!

09:49.840 --> 09:50.900
Don't come closer!

09:50.960 --> 09:51.890
Or I'll kill her!

09:52.080 --> 09:52.740
Ke Yixiong,

09:53.220 --> 09:54.030
calm down.

09:57.910 --> 09:58.640
Second Aunt.

10:00.200 --> 10:01.150
It's me, Junbao.

10:01.840 --> 10:02.720
Junbao?

10:03.150 --> 10:04.350
You've grown so tall.

10:05.390 --> 10:05.840
Why...

10:06.690 --> 10:07.880
Why are you here?

10:08.870 --> 10:09.600
Second Aunt,

10:10.270 --> 10:11.440
please help me.

10:14.750 --> 10:15.670
I'm not stupid.

10:16.010 --> 10:17.360
When that old man Du Chengrong

10:17.360 --> 10:19.090
called me to Shengcheng, I knew

10:19.550 --> 10:21.150
I wouldn't be able to go back.

10:21.360 --> 10:22.360
Even without you,

10:23.320 --> 10:24.870
he could easily kill me.

10:25.670 --> 10:26.270
Xia Ziyu!

10:26.960 --> 10:27.690
Let my mom go.

10:28.000 --> 10:30.600
And I'll help you
negotiate with Du Chengrong.

10:32.790 --> 10:33.750
How touching.

10:36.080 --> 10:37.080
Negotiate?

10:38.250 --> 10:38.750
I told you that,

10:38.750 --> 10:41.000
since I'm here,
it's impossible for me to go back.

10:41.000 --> 10:41.670
I came...

10:42.670 --> 10:45.000
to settle things with you
once and for all.

10:46.790 --> 10:48.650
I know the police are coming soon.

10:49.630 --> 10:51.490
But who are they coming to arrest?

10:52.510 --> 10:53.240
Vivi?

10:53.670 --> 10:54.790
Or Xia Ziyu?

10:56.600 --> 10:57.080
Xia Xiaolan,

10:57.080 --> 10:58.270
look at my face.

11:00.960 --> 11:01.870
Who should I be?

11:09.870 --> 11:10.600
Who you are

11:11.840 --> 11:13.200
should be up to you.

11:14.200 --> 11:15.030
Actually, for me,

11:15.030 --> 11:15.910
who I am hasn't mattered

11:15.910 --> 11:16.790
for a long time.

11:18.870 --> 11:20.200
As long as I can survive,

11:21.320 --> 11:22.670
I can be anyone.

11:24.270 --> 11:25.730
Xia Xiaolan, you're smart

11:26.550 --> 11:27.210
and pretty,

11:28.510 --> 11:31.570
and you've always
gotten the better of me, haven't you?

11:32.360 --> 11:33.870
But I'm Xia Ziyu!

11:36.200 --> 11:38.060
You figured it out a long time ago.

11:38.200 --> 11:39.200
I changed my face,

11:39.840 --> 11:40.480
changed my name,

11:40.480 --> 11:41.270
and even

11:42.080 --> 11:43.550
changed my dominant hand.

11:44.720 --> 11:45.750
But there are many things

11:45.750 --> 11:47.120
I can't forget.

11:50.910 --> 11:52.910
I can't forget the child I lost.

11:54.000 --> 11:56.390
I can't forget the home I can't return to.

11:57.670 --> 11:58.240
Yes,

12:00.290 --> 12:02.670
I'm the one who had someone
break your hand.

12:02.670 --> 12:04.870
I'm the one who's always been against you.

12:04.870 --> 12:07.000
I'm the one who had someone poison you!

12:08.510 --> 12:10.710
I just don't want you to have a good life.

12:11.640 --> 12:13.120
I just want you to taste

12:13.120 --> 12:14.450
the feeling of failure.

12:16.440 --> 12:17.640
Come on, Xia Xiaolan.

12:18.600 --> 12:19.030
Beg me.

12:20.360 --> 12:21.320
Kneel and beg me.

12:22.510 --> 12:23.840
Beg me to let your mom go.

12:26.750 --> 12:27.240
Kneel.

12:36.550 --> 12:37.400
Xia Ziyu,

12:41.280 --> 12:42.920
if I really kneel and beg you,

12:44.970 --> 12:46.030
will you let her go?

12:47.080 --> 12:48.440
Show some sincerity.

12:59.390 --> 13:02.240
Have you ever heard of
"the power of money"?

13:05.270 --> 13:06.270
Are you crazy?

13:07.720 --> 13:08.720
Ke Yixiong, do it!

13:11.240 --> 13:12.120
Do it!

13:18.150 --> 13:19.080
What do you mean?

13:23.360 --> 13:25.160
Money can't change everything,

13:25.360 --> 13:26.820
but it can change a person.

13:30.200 --> 13:31.600
Ke Yixiong, what are you doing?

13:31.600 --> 13:32.260
Ke Yixiong!

13:37.530 --> 13:39.280
Second Aunt, I'm Junbao.

13:40.240 --> 13:41.120
Junbao?

13:41.260 --> 13:42.540
You've grown so tall.

13:47.360 --> 13:48.090
Second Aunt,

13:48.240 --> 13:49.360
please help me.

13:57.850 --> 13:58.510
He fainted.

14:02.200 --> 14:03.400
What's going on here?

14:03.720 --> 14:04.180
Mr. Liu,

14:04.670 --> 14:05.710
this is Ke Yixiong.

14:05.710 --> 14:07.220
We finally caught this guy.

14:07.220 --> 14:07.750
Mrs. Liu,

14:08.100 --> 14:09.320
we need to cooperate with Xiaolan

14:09.320 --> 14:10.380
and finish the act.

14:14.480 --> 14:15.410
Where is Junbao?

14:25.030 --> 14:26.080
Xia Xiaolan

14:26.630 --> 14:28.160
really underestimated me.

14:28.840 --> 14:30.570
Trying to buy me off with money?

14:31.960 --> 14:32.820
Let me tell you,

14:33.720 --> 14:35.480
I just want to kill Xia Xiaolan.

14:37.320 --> 14:38.780
Unfortunately, your plan

14:38.790 --> 14:39.610
has failed.

14:47.480 --> 14:48.270
I advise you

14:49.250 --> 14:50.780
to think it over carefully.

15:01.440 --> 15:02.100
Zhang Qing.

15:03.630 --> 15:05.490
He took Du Chengrong's territory

15:06.360 --> 15:08.090
and died in a traffic accident.

15:09.510 --> 15:10.170
Xu Chengye.

15:10.670 --> 15:12.270
He took Du Chengrong's woman

15:12.320 --> 15:14.120
and disappeared 2 months later.

15:14.270 --> 15:15.000
Wu Tianhao.

15:15.440 --> 15:17.640
He didn't follow Du Chengrong's orders

15:17.840 --> 15:19.370
and accidentally drowned.

15:20.670 --> 15:21.600
What do you mean?

15:22.550 --> 15:24.670
When Du Chengrong asked Xia Ziyu
to come back,

15:24.670 --> 15:26.860
he never intended for her to return alive.

15:26.860 --> 15:27.590
Helping her?

15:28.620 --> 15:29.240
Have you ever thought about

15:29.240 --> 15:30.900
how she has been treating you?

15:37.240 --> 15:38.640
If you cooperate with us,

15:39.150 --> 15:40.080
finish this act,

15:41.030 --> 15:42.790
and turn yourself in to the police,

15:42.790 --> 15:44.390
you'll at least have a chance

15:44.720 --> 15:46.320
to reunite with your mother.

15:55.280 --> 15:56.010
Are you okay?

15:56.960 --> 15:57.600
Xia Ziyu,

15:57.960 --> 15:59.290
do you think I'm stupid?

16:00.080 --> 16:02.240
If Du Chengrong can kill you,

16:02.240 --> 16:03.510
he can kill me too!

16:04.600 --> 16:06.000
I'm just a supporting role.

16:06.000 --> 16:06.960
My part is done.

16:07.390 --> 16:09.030
You main characters can continue.

16:09.030 --> 16:09.560
Goodbye.

16:09.750 --> 16:10.280
Goodbye.

16:11.000 --> 16:11.530
Goodbye.

16:11.790 --> 16:12.240
San,

16:12.670 --> 16:13.600
take my mom away.

16:13.720 --> 16:14.580
Nobody leaves!

16:15.200 --> 16:16.060
Nobody leaves!

16:16.750 --> 16:17.480
Xia Xiaolan,

16:17.750 --> 16:18.510
go to hell!

16:18.910 --> 16:19.510
Xiaolan!

16:23.010 --> 16:23.960
Mom, let's go.

16:28.640 --> 16:29.150
Xia Xiaolan,

16:29.150 --> 16:31.280
you think you've won again, don't you?

16:31.960 --> 16:33.720
I know you want me to go to jail.

16:35.140 --> 16:36.740
But do you have any evidence?

16:37.510 --> 16:38.600
I am Vivi now.

16:38.600 --> 16:39.750
I'm no longer

16:39.750 --> 16:40.720
Xia Ziyu!

16:43.150 --> 16:43.840
Xia Ziyu.

16:46.430 --> 16:47.430
You're too naive.

17:08.920 --> 17:09.310
Ziyu.

17:09.829 --> 17:10.490
Xia Junbao?

17:11.069 --> 17:12.750
Junbao, she is not your sister.

17:12.750 --> 17:13.790
She is Vivi. Give it to me.

17:13.790 --> 17:14.849
Vivi is my sister.

17:14.880 --> 17:15.740
She is Xia Ziyu.

17:16.160 --> 17:17.400
Ziyu, let's go.

17:17.530 --> 17:19.130
The police are already here.

17:20.200 --> 17:20.880
Xia Ziyu!

17:23.530 --> 17:24.660
Where are you going?

17:25.700 --> 17:26.190
Junbao.

17:38.830 --> 17:39.560
Xia Xiaolan.

17:41.680 --> 17:42.400
If things

17:42.400 --> 17:43.880
don't go your way,

17:45.720 --> 17:47.720
will you still remember who you are?

17:48.680 --> 17:49.190
I will.

17:51.400 --> 17:53.110
Don't push things to the extreme.

17:53.110 --> 17:54.640
Leave some room for others.

17:56.510 --> 17:58.170
We won't see each other again,

18:00.200 --> 18:00.880
Cousin.

18:02.880 --> 18:03.680
Take her away!

18:21.720 --> 18:22.520
It's all over.

18:23.920 --> 18:24.650
Let's go too.

18:26.480 --> 18:26.880
Okay.

18:42.200 --> 18:43.460
Why are you still counting?

18:43.460 --> 18:44.890
Can I leave today or not?

18:44.920 --> 18:46.400
Yixiong, what's the rush?

18:46.850 --> 18:48.440
I will definitely let you go today.

18:48.440 --> 18:49.350
Then let me go.

18:49.350 --> 18:50.810
What are you dawdling for?

18:54.920 --> 18:55.380
Freeze!

18:56.320 --> 18:58.080
Freeze! Get down!

18:58.110 --> 18:59.310
Put down the suitcase!

18:59.310 --> 19:00.350
Put down the suitcase!

19:00.350 --> 19:01.610
Put down the suitcase!

19:01.960 --> 19:02.490
Get down!

19:03.550 --> 19:04.240
Get down!

19:04.550 --> 19:05.510
Get down!

19:08.790 --> 19:10.120
Hands behind your head!

19:11.160 --> 19:12.490
-Take them away!
-Move!

19:37.710 --> 19:38.630
[Xia Xiaolan]

19:41.510 --> 19:42.830
[Xia Xiaolan]

19:43.140 --> 19:45.100
[Golden Sands Pool]

19:44.680 --> 19:46.210
It is because of such hatred

19:46.830 --> 19:48.690
that Xia Ziyu has come to this day.

19:49.550 --> 19:51.200
This is Xia Ziyu's recording.

19:51.200 --> 19:52.400
It contains her own

19:52.420 --> 19:53.640
confession of her crimes.

19:53.640 --> 19:54.000
Okay.

19:55.200 --> 19:55.590
Mom.

19:56.030 --> 19:56.440
Thank you so much

19:56.440 --> 19:58.100
for your help with the police.

19:58.790 --> 19:59.320
Are you alright?

19:59.320 --> 19:59.920
Thank you.

20:00.030 --> 20:00.590
We're fine.

20:00.590 --> 20:01.190
Thank you.

20:01.310 --> 20:01.910
It's okay.

20:03.000 --> 20:03.930
Are you alright?

20:10.830 --> 20:11.560
Are you okay?

20:12.070 --> 20:13.410
I'm fine. Thank you.

20:14.830 --> 20:16.030
I'm glad you're okay.

20:18.310 --> 20:19.710
Why are you staring at me?

20:19.830 --> 20:20.590
Don't worry.

20:20.720 --> 20:21.920
I'm a principled man.

20:21.920 --> 20:22.400
I wouldn't lay a finger

20:22.400 --> 20:23.730
on someone else's wife.

20:24.860 --> 20:25.880
But if I hear

20:25.880 --> 20:27.200
that you treat her badly,

20:27.200 --> 20:28.000
just you wait.

20:29.700 --> 20:30.630
Anyway,

20:31.590 --> 20:32.720
thank you for today.

20:38.880 --> 20:39.410
Alright.

20:39.870 --> 20:41.640
Call me if you need anything.

20:43.000 --> 20:43.530
Bye-bye.

20:44.720 --> 20:45.270
Goodbye.

20:47.030 --> 20:47.560
Alright.

20:47.960 --> 20:48.490
Let's go.

20:48.680 --> 20:49.210
Let's go.

20:49.400 --> 20:49.930
Let's go.

20:52.350 --> 20:52.860
Let me go!

20:52.860 --> 20:53.510
Get in the car!

20:53.510 --> 20:53.980
Let me go!

20:53.980 --> 20:54.780
Get in the car!

20:57.200 --> 20:58.460
Junbao is still young.

20:58.690 --> 20:59.550
See if there is any way

20:59.550 --> 21:00.270
to help him.

21:01.070 --> 21:01.440
Okay.

21:16.800 --> 21:18.590
The construction
of the Shengcheng Cross-River Bridge

21:18.590 --> 21:20.450
was completed ahead of schedule.

21:20.640 --> 21:22.200
After three years of construction,

21:22.200 --> 21:23.150
the cross-river bridge connecting
the north and south districts

21:23.150 --> 21:24.110
of Shengcheng

21:24.310 --> 21:26.310
officially opens to traffic today.

21:26.440 --> 21:28.170
The bridge is 1,200 meters long

21:28.400 --> 21:29.550
and designed with two-way four lanes.

21:29.550 --> 21:30.310
We're back.

21:30.510 --> 21:31.110
Granny Yu.

21:32.680 --> 21:33.610
You're all here?

21:35.030 --> 21:36.630
I told you to come back early,

21:36.830 --> 21:38.230
but none of you listened.

21:38.800 --> 21:40.130
You saw all this coming.

21:40.590 --> 21:41.400
Exactly.

21:43.240 --> 21:44.570
Don't just stand there.

21:45.240 --> 21:46.310
Sit down and eat.

21:46.400 --> 21:47.070
Okay.

21:47.960 --> 21:50.490
Production efficiency
has increased by 40%.

21:50.960 --> 21:52.350
Xiaolan, hand the chopsticks around.

21:52.350 --> 21:52.750
Okay.

21:53.170 --> 21:54.000
This move

21:54.050 --> 21:55.750
has set a benchmark
for the transformation and upgrading

21:55.750 --> 21:56.880
of old enterprises.

21:57.640 --> 21:58.570
Pass them along.

21:59.930 --> 22:00.530
Thank you.

22:01.920 --> 22:02.310
Here.

22:03.350 --> 22:03.880
Alright.

22:04.240 --> 22:05.370
Let's start eating.

22:05.480 --> 22:05.830
Okay.

22:06.830 --> 22:07.760
Have a dumpling.

22:09.480 --> 22:09.830
Here.

22:10.160 --> 22:11.360
Thank you, Granny Yu.

22:11.480 --> 22:11.830
Okay.

22:12.790 --> 22:13.920
Peace is a blessing.

22:14.550 --> 22:15.150
Granny Yu.

22:18.480 --> 22:19.160
This

22:19.750 --> 22:21.550
is a letter from Uncle Xu for you.

22:21.550 --> 22:23.000
Liu Jianjun and Wang Xiaofang, students

22:23.000 --> 22:25.060
from Shengcheng No.1 High School...

22:25.310 --> 22:25.750
Eat up.

22:26.510 --> 22:28.840
Won gold and silver medals respectively,

22:29.000 --> 22:30.680
setting the best record

22:30.680 --> 22:32.430
for our city in this competition.

22:32.430 --> 22:33.720
The Ministry of Education stated

22:33.720 --> 22:35.110
that it will step up efforts to cultivate

22:35.110 --> 22:36.310
innovative talents.

22:37.270 --> 22:39.470
That's all for this edition of the news.

22:39.680 --> 22:40.720
Thank you for watching.

22:40.720 --> 22:41.250
Goodbye.

22:44.480 --> 22:45.410
Welcome to Luna.

22:45.580 --> 22:46.440
Please come in.

22:46.880 --> 22:47.680
Luna's Story.

22:49.350 --> 22:50.210
I didn't expect

22:50.640 --> 22:52.440
we'd actually open 50 branches.

22:53.030 --> 22:53.590
Xiaolan,

22:54.440 --> 22:55.590
do you still remember

22:55.590 --> 22:57.350
the wholesale market back then?

22:57.350 --> 22:58.000
I do.

22:58.680 --> 22:59.440
At that time,

22:59.720 --> 23:01.520
you were just a small wholesaler

23:01.640 --> 23:02.590
with a pile of

23:02.590 --> 23:03.400
unsold stock.

23:03.920 --> 23:04.510
And I

23:04.680 --> 23:06.010
was a small stall owner.

23:06.070 --> 23:06.730
Some people

23:06.740 --> 23:08.940
wouldn't even wholesale clothes to me.

23:09.160 --> 23:10.480
But even then I knew

23:11.000 --> 23:13.160
we'd have a different future.

23:13.590 --> 23:14.850
Thinking about it now,

23:15.350 --> 23:16.750
it's really incredible.

23:17.440 --> 23:18.170
Xia Xiaolan,

23:18.880 --> 23:20.080
you are my lucky star.

23:21.070 --> 23:22.590
I wouldn't call myself a lucky star.

23:22.590 --> 23:24.070
I'm just not afraid of difficulties,

23:24.070 --> 23:25.730
and I dare to pursue my dreams.

23:26.680 --> 23:27.880
We have 50 stores now.

23:28.240 --> 23:28.770
Xiaolan,

23:29.440 --> 23:31.040
do you have any other dreams?

23:31.240 --> 23:31.840
Of course.

23:32.920 --> 23:34.110
I'm Xia Xiaolan.

23:34.620 --> 23:36.290
How could I stop here?

23:37.640 --> 23:39.880
As for my next dream,

23:41.510 --> 23:42.510
just wait and see.

23:42.830 --> 23:43.760
Do you remember?

23:43.790 --> 23:45.480
Open your mouth.

23:45.550 --> 23:46.000
I remember.

23:46.000 --> 23:46.800
What's wrong?

23:48.550 --> 23:49.510
Isn't that Xia Xiaolan?

23:49.510 --> 23:51.240
You really like watching this.

23:52.550 --> 23:53.880
Eat first. Come on.

23:57.000 --> 23:58.260
Ziyu is my real sister.

23:58.830 --> 24:00.640
She said she could give me a good life.

24:00.640 --> 24:01.440
When she ran away back then,

24:01.440 --> 24:02.430
did she ever care about you?

24:02.430 --> 24:03.440
When she was living a good life,

24:03.440 --> 24:04.550
did she think about you?

24:04.550 --> 24:05.610
She is your sister?

24:06.070 --> 24:07.200
Go find her then.

24:07.550 --> 24:08.270
Go find her.

24:08.510 --> 24:09.110
Go.

24:09.610 --> 24:11.030
I wouldn't call myself a lucky star.

24:11.030 --> 24:12.440
I'm just not afraid of difficulties,

24:12.440 --> 24:14.100
and I dare to pursue my dreams.

24:14.840 --> 24:16.040
We have 50 stores now.

24:37.270 --> 24:38.070
You know what?

24:38.960 --> 24:40.240
When I first came here,

24:41.310 --> 24:42.200
I could often feel

24:42.200 --> 24:44.000
the presence of another person.

24:45.550 --> 24:46.640
She told me

24:47.070 --> 24:48.800
she didn't want to be slandered

24:49.310 --> 24:51.770
and had no intention
of committing suicide.

24:51.790 --> 24:53.240
She also wanted to go to a broader world

24:53.240 --> 24:54.100
and take a look.

24:55.720 --> 24:57.000
But later on,

24:57.960 --> 24:59.490
I couldn't feel her anymore

25:00.590 --> 25:02.590
and couldn't hold on to my past self.

25:04.240 --> 25:05.310
Sometimes,

25:06.550 --> 25:07.070
it really felt like

25:07.070 --> 25:08.240
what Xia Ziyu said—

25:10.350 --> 25:12.010
I couldn't remember who I was.

25:16.720 --> 25:18.200
But you didn't stop

25:19.270 --> 25:20.730
because of the confusion.

25:21.480 --> 25:22.810
You kept moving forward

25:23.310 --> 25:24.910
and gained new experiences.

25:25.310 --> 25:26.350
Although you can't feel

25:26.350 --> 25:27.410
that girl anymore,

25:28.750 --> 25:30.350
you've shaped who you are now

25:31.480 --> 25:32.430
and realized

25:33.000 --> 25:35.200
the dream both of you wanted to achieve.

25:36.350 --> 25:37.640
I used to be afraid.

25:39.070 --> 25:39.750
I was afraid that all of this

25:39.750 --> 25:41.010
would become nothing.

25:44.750 --> 25:46.070
But now I'm not afraid.

25:47.550 --> 25:48.410
Because I know,

25:49.680 --> 25:51.200
even if I start over,

25:52.850 --> 25:54.580
I can definitely do a great job.

25:59.640 --> 26:00.680
It's just that...

26:02.960 --> 26:04.560
I still worry occasionally.

26:08.640 --> 26:09.200
What if...

26:09.200 --> 26:09.720
I said

26:11.200 --> 26:12.460
there was no "what if."

26:13.550 --> 26:14.810
Even if that day comes,

26:16.510 --> 26:17.440
I will find you.

26:40.080 --> 26:42.090
[A few days later]

26:42.120 --> 26:43.690
[Qi Hang Property]

26:46.350 --> 26:46.830
Hou Qi.

26:47.880 --> 26:48.940
Later, I want to...

26:50.200 --> 26:50.750
I want...

26:52.070 --> 26:53.600
You want to ask me to a movie?

26:53.720 --> 26:55.450
Yes, I want to ask you to a movie.

26:55.550 --> 26:56.180
Well,

26:56.720 --> 26:58.050
let's eat hot pot first.

26:58.440 --> 26:59.090
Hello, Ms. Xia.

26:59.090 --> 26:59.950
Happy New Year.

27:04.190 --> 27:05.580
Happy New Year, Ms. Xia.

27:05.600 --> 27:06.460
Happy New Year.

27:07.480 --> 27:08.000
Ms. Xia.

27:08.590 --> 27:10.160
Here is the information
for next week's project.

27:10.160 --> 27:11.220
I've sorted it out.

27:11.550 --> 27:11.960
Also,

27:11.960 --> 27:13.110
you have a meeting
on the 10th with the architects

27:13.110 --> 27:14.350
from Shengcheng Design Institute.

27:14.350 --> 27:16.000
Should I book you the evening flight

27:16.000 --> 27:16.720
for that day?

27:16.720 --> 27:17.110
Sure.

27:17.680 --> 27:18.790
Tomorrow is New Year's Day.

27:18.790 --> 27:19.920
You should go home soon.

27:19.920 --> 27:20.270
Okay.

27:20.590 --> 27:22.000
Happy New Year, Ms. Xia.

27:22.550 --> 27:23.410
Happy New Year.

27:23.510 --> 27:23.920
Okay.

27:24.350 --> 27:25.350
I'll get going then.

27:25.350 --> 27:25.750
Bye-bye.

27:25.750 --> 27:26.280
Bye-bye.

27:27.000 --> 27:27.530
Bye-bye.

27:37.000 --> 27:37.730
What's this?

27:38.690 --> 27:40.620
There's no return address on this.

27:42.510 --> 27:43.160
Ye...

27:45.790 --> 27:46.720
Ye Xiaoqiong?

27:48.740 --> 27:49.510
It seems she has already

27:49.510 --> 27:51.110
found a place to settle down.

27:51.480 --> 27:52.160
Let's leave too.

27:52.160 --> 27:52.690
Let's go.

27:56.510 --> 27:56.960
Wait.

28:01.160 --> 28:01.690
Let's go.

28:42.750 --> 28:43.680
Come on!

28:43.940 --> 28:47.720
Happy New Year!

28:57.310 --> 28:58.200
You're going to

28:58.550 --> 29:00.810
build an amusement park in Qiong Island?

29:01.880 --> 29:02.400
Yes.

29:03.890 --> 29:04.970
Guess why.

29:08.160 --> 29:09.290
To share happiness?

29:10.960 --> 29:11.760
Close enough.

29:12.480 --> 29:13.400
Although I don't remember

29:13.400 --> 29:14.400
many things now,

29:15.110 --> 29:16.310
I can tell that

29:17.100 --> 29:18.830
Xia Xiaolan before coming here

29:19.160 --> 29:20.890
and Xia Xiaolan in Dahe Village

29:21.030 --> 29:21.890
were not happy.

29:24.200 --> 29:25.350
But now,

29:26.160 --> 29:27.070
I have love,

29:27.480 --> 29:28.110
family,

29:28.640 --> 29:29.200
friends,

29:29.640 --> 29:30.370
and a career.

29:30.920 --> 29:32.270
I am very happy

29:32.590 --> 29:33.720
and very satisfied.

29:35.200 --> 29:36.930
And I want to share this feeling

29:37.000 --> 29:37.960
with others.

29:38.830 --> 29:39.590
Maybe

29:39.960 --> 29:40.750
that's the meaning

29:40.750 --> 29:41.750
of my coming here.

29:44.350 --> 29:45.550
And an amusement park

29:46.030 --> 29:48.440
is a place full of happiness.

29:49.790 --> 29:50.850
This is the best way

29:51.240 --> 29:52.570
I can think of right now.

30:05.440 --> 30:07.300
Although I don't really remember

30:07.600 --> 30:09.600
what Shengcheng looked like later,

30:11.240 --> 30:11.960
I guess

30:13.240 --> 30:15.170
it must be more beautiful than now.

30:23.310 --> 30:24.040
Look at that.

30:25.060 --> 30:27.980
Doesn't it look like the gears of fate?

30:28.880 --> 30:30.240
There must be many people

30:30.240 --> 30:30.840
there now,

30:31.480 --> 30:32.940
waiting for the countdown

30:33.270 --> 30:34.600
to welcome the New Year.

30:38.640 --> 30:39.400
10,

30:40.720 --> 30:41.590
9,

30:42.720 --> 30:43.510
8,

30:44.750 --> 30:45.550
7,

30:46.680 --> 30:47.590
6,

30:48.750 --> 30:49.590
5,

30:50.750 --> 30:51.550
4...

31:07.470 --> 31:08.130
Xiaolan?

31:12.130 --> 31:13.460
What's wrong, Xiaolan?

31:17.080 --> 31:17.680
Xiaolan?

31:23.650 --> 31:24.310
Zhou Cheng.

31:25.780 --> 31:26.480
I'm sorry.

31:27.640 --> 31:28.680
This might be

31:31.130 --> 31:32.510
the end of my time.

31:53.950 --> 31:59.320
♪ Watching the flowers fall,
lonely I ask the night sky ♪

32:00.320 --> 32:05.070
♪ Is spring hazy where you are? ♪

32:07.400 --> 32:11.820
♪ Time is upside down,
the seasons intertwine ♪

32:13.040 --> 32:19.070
♪ Fate seems to want us to stay silent ♪

32:20.360 --> 32:26.070
♪ Time is so stingy,
even memories are hard to keep ♪

32:20.750 --> 32:21.550
3,

32:22.310 --> 32:23.110
2,

32:23.750 --> 32:24.550
1!

32:25.550 --> 32:28.000
Happy New Year!

32:27.760 --> 32:34.620
♪ But I still remember
our promises of love ♪

32:35.370 --> 32:37.320
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

32:37.460 --> 32:41.730
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

32:39.890 --> 32:40.420
Xiaolan!

32:42.160 --> 32:44.570
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

32:44.720 --> 32:49.330
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

32:49.680 --> 32:53.640
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

32:52.640 --> 32:53.300
Zhou Cheng?

32:53.770 --> 32:57.820
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

32:58.770 --> 33:02.440
♪ We will finally reunite ♪

33:18.500 --> 33:24.330
♪ We fight against the wind
and challenge fate ♪

33:22.410 --> 33:24.610
The original me isn't in this timeline.

33:24.850 --> 33:25.650
and in that timeline,

33:25.120 --> 33:30.270
♪ We are meant
to have the freedom to love ♪

33:25.680 --> 33:27.880
the current you wouldn't exist either.

33:28.960 --> 33:29.820
I'll find a way.

33:30.790 --> 33:32.250
I'll definitely find you.

33:32.370 --> 33:37.100
♪ No matter how absurd the world is,
or how time toys with us ♪

33:32.790 --> 33:33.590
But...

33:33.790 --> 33:34.720
you haven't seen

33:34.720 --> 33:35.650
me in that world.

33:36.440 --> 33:37.270
How would you know

33:37.270 --> 33:38.030
if that's me?

33:37.570 --> 33:44.930
♪ I will still hold your hand
until we grow old ♪

33:39.070 --> 33:40.130
As long as I see you,

33:40.790 --> 33:41.920
I'll recognize you,

33:42.440 --> 33:43.970
just like when we first met.

33:45.200 --> 33:46.440
When you see me then,

33:45.480 --> 33:48.430
♪ Time is so stingy ♪

33:46.750 --> 33:48.240
shout my name,

33:48.450 --> 33:51.800
♪ It takes away even the memories ♪

33:48.680 --> 33:50.080
and I'll know who you are.

33:51.000 --> 33:52.240
Xiaolan!

33:52.690 --> 33:55.300
♪ But I still remember ♪

33:55.490 --> 33:59.770
♪ The promises of love ♪

33:59.970 --> 34:02.430
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

34:02.450 --> 34:07.160
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

34:06.640 --> 34:07.920
Xia Xiaolan!

34:07.190 --> 34:09.750
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

34:09.770 --> 34:14.320
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

34:12.190 --> 34:14.280
You must remember our promise!

34:14.800 --> 34:18.570
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

34:18.590 --> 34:22.800
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

34:23.440 --> 34:27.820
♪ We will finally reunite ♪

34:28.969 --> 34:35.520
♪ I believe that our mutual calls
can break through the heavens ♪

34:35.730 --> 34:39.150
♪ When even the cold world turns gentle ♪

34:39.170 --> 34:44.770
♪ We will finally embrace
and stay together ♪

34:41.230 --> 34:41.889
Zhou Cheng,

34:43.150 --> 34:44.630
before I came here,

34:45.480 --> 34:46.760
the dreams I dared to dream
were very small.

34:45.980 --> 34:48.429
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

34:48.460 --> 34:53.170
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

34:49.030 --> 34:50.800
Just staying alive

34:51.880 --> 34:53.190
was exhausting enough.

34:53.190 --> 34:55.750
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

34:54.590 --> 34:55.440
And now

34:55.780 --> 35:00.320
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

34:56.440 --> 34:58.320
I want to become a great architect

34:59.390 --> 35:01.540
and build many, many beautiful buildings.

35:00.800 --> 35:04.570
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

35:02.760 --> 35:03.360
Of course,

35:04.440 --> 35:06.070
it includes our own home.

35:04.600 --> 35:08.800
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

35:09.710 --> 35:14.280
♪ Together, forever ♪

35:33.670 --> 35:35.930
I'm becoming braver about living freely

35:35.960 --> 35:37.690
and looking toward the future—

35:38.630 --> 35:41.260
not just because I've been given
a second chance at life,

35:41.260 --> 35:42.500
but because all the things

35:42.500 --> 35:44.160
I once had no one to confide in,

35:44.400 --> 35:46.000
the dreams no one supported,

35:46.510 --> 35:49.240
and the pain and vulnerability
no one understood

35:49.280 --> 35:51.080
have all been gently held by you.

36:29.960 --> 36:30.620
Zhou Cheng,

36:31.550 --> 36:33.480
thank you for appearing in my life,

36:33.840 --> 36:35.170
thank you for your help,

36:35.960 --> 36:37.490
and thank you for your love.

36:38.360 --> 36:39.320
This love

36:40.110 --> 36:41.670
healed the coward in me

36:43.230 --> 36:45.360
and made me the Xia Xiaolan I am today.

36:47.190 --> 36:47.960
I believe

36:48.920 --> 36:50.780
no matter where I am in the future,

36:51.280 --> 36:52.550
the love you gave me

36:52.920 --> 36:54.480
will always accompany me.

36:55.630 --> 36:56.960
And please believe that

36:57.840 --> 36:59.500
even if we drift apart one day,

36:59.960 --> 37:01.890
I will try my best to respond to you,

37:02.630 --> 37:04.160
just as you called out to me.

37:10.400 --> 37:11.710
Do you know what's most important

37:11.710 --> 37:13.110
when signing a contract?

37:13.550 --> 37:14.880
The most important thing

37:14.880 --> 37:16.110
is to first verify

37:16.110 --> 37:17.510
if the party you're signing with

37:17.510 --> 37:18.240
is reliable.

37:18.550 --> 37:19.360
Only after that

37:19.360 --> 37:21.880
do you verify
the specific terms and clauses.

37:21.880 --> 37:23.740
This time, we are signing with...

37:23.960 --> 37:24.710
the government,

37:24.710 --> 37:25.840
so they won't play

37:25.840 --> 37:27.190
word games to set traps.

37:31.280 --> 37:32.210
The contract...

38:00.880 --> 38:02.740
This contract was tampered with.

38:02.800 --> 38:04.420
It was printed according to the format

38:04.420 --> 38:05.970
we agreed on before.

38:06.230 --> 38:08.090
There shouldn't be any problems.

38:11.110 --> 38:12.910
Look at the contract you signed!

38:13.150 --> 38:14.110
Look at how the joint liability clauses

38:14.110 --> 38:14.840
are written!

38:15.590 --> 38:16.050
Ms. Xia.

38:16.280 --> 38:18.470
There's a whole room of people waiting

38:18.490 --> 38:19.670
to go home for the weekend.

38:19.670 --> 38:20.840
I can't leave

38:21.140 --> 38:21.840
until the contract is signed,

38:21.840 --> 38:22.710
so they can't leave too.

38:22.710 --> 38:23.570
How about we...

38:24.150 --> 38:25.410
Mr. Jia, you really are

38:25.760 --> 38:27.690
so considerate of your employees.

38:28.030 --> 38:29.400
Can you think carefully about

38:29.400 --> 38:30.480
what kind of person

38:30.480 --> 38:31.280
you want to be

38:31.280 --> 38:32.840
and what kind of life you want to live?

38:32.840 --> 38:33.710
Can you

38:33.710 --> 38:35.040
get your head straight?

38:38.450 --> 38:39.050
Mr. Wang?

38:51.670 --> 38:52.200
Mr. Chen.

38:53.840 --> 38:54.670
Why is it you?

38:57.150 --> 38:58.480
I have something to say.

39:02.000 --> 39:02.460
Come in.

39:07.480 --> 39:08.010
Mr. Chen.

39:08.920 --> 39:09.690
These pieces of evidence

39:09.690 --> 39:11.490
are enough to prove my innocence

39:11.710 --> 39:12.400
and to show that Mr. Wang,

39:12.400 --> 39:14.660
Wang Tianlin, committed embezzlement.

39:17.230 --> 39:18.440
I said last time

39:19.000 --> 39:20.840
I wouldn't pursue this with you anymore.

39:20.840 --> 39:22.370
You could have just let it go

39:22.510 --> 39:24.240
and started over with a new job.

39:24.760 --> 39:25.880
So why do you still insist

39:25.880 --> 39:27.340
on exposing Wang Tianlin?

39:27.630 --> 39:28.280
For you,

39:29.480 --> 39:31.680
this probably not only has no benefits,

39:34.030 --> 39:35.150
but could also provoke

39:35.150 --> 39:37.810
retaliation
from those with vested interests.

39:38.320 --> 39:38.850
Mr. Chen.

39:39.710 --> 39:41.840
I used to be a cowardly person

39:42.320 --> 39:44.000
who, because of fear of losing things,

39:44.000 --> 39:45.840
always overthought everything

39:46.190 --> 39:47.590
and was overly cautious.

39:48.550 --> 39:49.550
But a few days ago,

39:50.960 --> 39:51.960
I had a dream.

39:54.230 --> 39:55.070
In the dream,

39:56.190 --> 39:57.510
I became someone else,

39:58.960 --> 39:59.960
someone who could

40:01.190 --> 40:02.670
enjoy life to the fullest

40:04.000 --> 40:05.860
and express her feelings freely.

40:09.230 --> 40:10.760
In the dream, I gained a lot,

40:11.760 --> 40:13.070
and I lost a lot too.

40:14.880 --> 40:16.080
Then the dream ended,

40:17.400 --> 40:18.800
and everything was gone.

40:20.670 --> 40:22.270
But I don't think it was fake.

40:23.630 --> 40:24.400
This dream

40:25.800 --> 40:26.800
gave me courage.

40:28.670 --> 40:29.480
So I plan

40:30.360 --> 40:31.890
to live bravely from now on.

40:34.000 --> 40:34.930
Bravely accept,

40:36.070 --> 40:37.000
bravely refuse,

40:38.280 --> 40:39.480
and bravely face fate

40:40.440 --> 40:42.370
and all the unknown arrangements.

40:47.190 --> 40:47.720
Xiaolan,

40:48.110 --> 40:49.020
we have submitted

40:49.020 --> 40:50.480
all the evidence and materials.

40:50.480 --> 40:51.190
I believe

40:51.510 --> 40:52.230
the law will give you a

40:52.230 --> 40:52.960
fair answer.

40:53.880 --> 40:54.540
Take my car.

40:54.590 --> 40:55.650
I'll send you back.

40:55.920 --> 40:56.440
No need.

40:56.880 --> 40:57.920
Thank you, Mr. Chen.

40:57.920 --> 40:59.380
I want to take a walk alone.

41:00.070 --> 41:00.600
Alright.

41:42.450 --> 41:43.510
How is it possible?

41:44.920 --> 41:45.850
Things like that

41:46.880 --> 41:48.010
won't happen again.

41:48.100 --> 41:48.670
Xiaolan.

41:50.310 --> 41:58.550
♪ Maybe all encounters in the world
are predetermined by destiny ♪

42:00.400 --> 42:05.170
♪ The opening and closing chapters
are written ♪

42:04.210 --> 42:04.760
Xiaolan.

42:06.120 --> 42:14.610
♪ From when we first met
till now, though much has changed ♪

42:08.230 --> 42:09.290
As long as I see you,

42:10.190 --> 42:12.050
I'll recognize you immediately.

42:12.510 --> 42:14.240
Just like the first time we met.

42:14.400 --> 42:15.630
When you see me then,

42:15.880 --> 42:17.360
shout my name,

42:16.260 --> 42:21.300
♪ Our hearts remain unchanged ♪

42:18.280 --> 42:19.680
and I'll know who you are.

42:21.710 --> 42:31.750
♪ Having a dream in your eyes,
and time passes by ♪

42:23.960 --> 42:24.400
Hello.

42:25.760 --> 42:26.590
Xia Xiaolan.

42:32.090 --> 42:36.750
♪ Yet I still love you the same ♪

42:37.410 --> 42:51.500
♪ After traveling through the crowds and dark tides,
we must embrace with the weight of the moment ♪
